{
  "video_id": "CXy1byguvJY",
  "title": "A new way to monitor vital signs (that can see through walls) | Dina Katabi",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13150.0,
      "end_time": 14325.0,
      "text": "When I was a kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14349.0,
      "end_time": 19249.0,
      "text": "I was, like many of you in this room, very much fascinated by Star Wars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19273.0,
      "end_time": 23749.0,
      "text": "and what fascinated me the most is this notion of the Force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23773.0,
      "end_time": 26883.0,
      "text": "this energy that connects all people and all objects"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26907.0,
      "end_time": 30325.0,
      "text": "and allows you to feel people that you can&#39;t even see."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30753.0,
      "end_time": 33841.0,
      "text": "And I remember many nights, I would be sitting at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33865.0,
      "end_time": 37835.0,
      "text": "just, like, concentrating and focusing, trying to feel the Force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38624.0,
      "end_time": 41187.0,
      "text": "and I didn&#39;t feel anything, don&#39;t worry."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41211.0,
      "end_time": 43680.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43920.0,
      "end_time": 45942.0,
      "text": "And later in life, I became a scientist."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45966.0,
      "end_time": 50679.0,
      "text": "I joined the MIT faculty and started working on wireless signals."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51184.0,
      "end_time": 54327.0,
      "text": "These are things like Wi-Fi or cellular systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54351.0,
      "end_time": 56702.0,
      "text": "and I did a lot of work in that domain."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57489.0,
      "end_time": 62770.0,
      "text": "But then, again, this Force thing kept nagging me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62102.0,
      "end_time": 64270.0,
      "text": "and at some point, I was just like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 64510.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68703.0,
      "text": "\"Wait a minute, these wireless signals -- they are like the Force.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68727.0,
      "end_time": 69921.0,
      "text": "So if you think about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69945.0,
      "end_time": 72576.0,
      "text": "wireless signals, they travel through space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72600.0,
      "end_time": 76800.0,
      "text": "they go through obstacles and walls and occlusions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76104.0,
      "end_time": 77345.0,
      "text": "and some of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77369.0,
      "end_time": 81519.0,
      "text": "they reflect off our bodies, because our bodies are full of water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81543.0,
      "end_time": 83749.0,
      "text": "and some of these minute reflections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83773.0,
      "end_time": 85300.0,
      "text": "they come back."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85550.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "And if, just if, I had a device that can just sense these minute reflections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92500.0,
      "end_time": 95330.0,
      "text": "then I would be able to feel people that I cannot see."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96444.0,
      "end_time": 100197.0,
      "text": "So I started working with my students on building such a device,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100221.0,
      "end_time": 103531.0,
      "text": "and I want to show you some of our early results."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 104584.0,
      "end_time": 106867.0,
      "text": "So here, you see my student standing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106891.0,
      "end_time": 108868.0,
      "text": "and here is our device."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108892.0,
      "end_time": 114502.0,
      "text": "And we are going to put the device in the other office, behind the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 114526.0,
      "end_time": 117342.0,
      "text": "and we are going to monitor him as he moves."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117367.0,
      "end_time": 121446.0,
      "text": "This red dot is tracking him using wireless signals."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122760.0,
      "end_time": 127544.0,
      "text": "And as you can see, the red dot is tracking his movements very accurately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 127568.0,
      "end_time": 132322.0,
      "text": "purely based on how his body interacts with the surrounding wireless signals."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 133631.0,
      "end_time": 135335.0,
      "text": "Pretty accurate, isn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 136702.0,
      "end_time": 138575.0,
      "text": "He has no wearables, nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 138599.0,
      "end_time": 141412.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 141437.0,
      "end_time": 143182.0,
      "text": "Now you might be wondering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 143206.0,
      "end_time": 146387.0,
      "text": "how is it possible that we can sense people"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 146412.0,
      "end_time": 150258.0,
      "text": "and track them, without any wearables, through walls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 150282.0,
      "end_time": 153648.0,
      "text": "and the easiest analogy to think about is radar."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 153672.0,
      "end_time": 155765.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure many of you have seen this picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 155789.0,
      "end_time": 157946.0,
      "text": "You transmit a wireless signal to the sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 157971.0,
      "end_time": 160939.0,
      "text": "it reflects off some airplane, comes back to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 160963.0,
      "end_time": 163304.0,
      "text": "and you start detecting these airplanes."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 164328.0,
      "end_time": 166272.0,
      "text": "But if it were just radar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166296.0,
      "end_time": 168548.0,
      "text": "then we would have this 50 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 169272.0,
      "end_time": 170977.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s not just radar."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 171285.0,
      "end_time": 173475.0,
      "text": "There are two key differences."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174229.0,
      "end_time": 175992.0,
      "text": "So the first difference, of course --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176160.0,
      "end_time": 179535.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t, like radar, just blast wireless power at somebody."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 179559.0,
      "end_time": 182286.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re going to fry them like if they were in a microwave."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182310.0,
      "end_time": 183460.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 184595.0,
      "end_time": 189660.0,
      "text": "So it means that you have to be able to deal with very weak signals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189684.0,
      "end_time": 192810.0,
      "text": "and that means that your device has to be very sensitive."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 194144.0,
      "end_time": 198275.0,
      "text": "The second difference is that, unlike the sky, where it&#39;s empty --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 198299.0,
      "end_time": 201443.0,
      "text": "if you are lucky, there is one airplane that you can catch there."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 201467.0,
      "end_time": 202809.0,
      "text": "Like, look at the room"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 202833.0,
      "end_time": 205721.0,
      "text": "and look how many objects and people there are."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 205745.0,
      "end_time": 209682.0,
      "text": "So in indoor environments, the signal not only reflects off the person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 209706.0,
      "end_time": 213499.0,
      "text": "if reflects off the person, off the floor, the ceiling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 213523.0,
      "end_time": 215745.0,
      "text": "off other people around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 215769.0,
      "end_time": 217752.0,
      "text": "and you get very complex reflections"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 217776.0,
      "end_time": 220507.0,
      "text": "where the same signal reflects off me and then off you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 220531.0,
      "end_time": 222769.0,
      "text": "and then off the ceiling, then off the floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 222793.0,
      "end_time": 225962.0,
      "text": "And you have to make sense of that mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 227993.0,
      "end_time": 229841.0,
      "text": "But we were lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 229866.0,
      "end_time": 232358.0,
      "text": "We were coming at the right time."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 233252.0,
      "end_time": 235124.0,
      "text": "So two things helped us."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 235148.0,
      "end_time": 239204.0,
      "text": "The first thing is radiotechnologies have evolved a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 239228.0,
      "end_time": 241300.0,
      "text": "and over the last decade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 241270.0,
      "end_time": 243337.0,
      "text": "radio technology became much more powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 243361.0,
      "end_time": 247970.0,
      "text": "so we were able to build very sensitive radios"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 247122.0,
      "end_time": 250479.0,
      "text": "that can sense weak and minute RF signals."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 251725.0,
      "end_time": 254763.0,
      "text": "The second thing: machine learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 254788.0,
      "end_time": 256788.0,
      "text": "So you keep hearing about machine learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 256812.0,
      "end_time": 259773.0,
      "text": "and there was a revolution of machine learning recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 259797.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260948.00000000003,
      "text": "in deep learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 260971.0,
      "end_time": 264741.0,
      "text": "and that allowed us to build machine-learning models"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 264765.0,
      "end_time": 268312.0,
      "text": "that can understand wireless signals and interpret them"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 268336.0,
      "end_time": 271841.0,
      "text": "so they would know what happened in the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 271865.0,
      "end_time": 275675.0,
      "text": "So if you think of it, the radio is like the ear of our device"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 275699.0,
      "end_time": 278278.0,
      "text": "and the machine learning is like the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 278302.0,
      "end_time": 282125.0,
      "text": "and together, they have a very powerful device."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 284108.0,
      "end_time": 289131.0,
      "text": "So what else can we sense about people using wireless signals?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 290458.0,
      "end_time": 291609.0,
      "text": "Sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 291633.0,
      "end_time": 294610.0,
      "text": "Sleep, actually, is something very dear to my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 294860.0,
      "end_time": 296130.0,
      "text": "because my sleep is a disaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 296370.0,
      "end_time": 297385.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 297409.0,
      "end_time": 300638.0,
      "text": "So one thing is when you start working on some physiological signal"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 300662.0,
      "end_time": 303320.0,
      "text": "and you discover that yours sucks."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 303908.0,
      "end_time": 307300.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 307344.0,
      "end_time": 309469.0,
      "text": "So you can see why we can capture sleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 309494.0,
      "end_time": 312760.0,
      "text": "because the person walks and the device sees him as he walks to bed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 312784.0,
      "end_time": 315580.0,
      "text": "when he stops tossing around in bed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 315830.0,
      "end_time": 316924.0,
      "text": "when he steps out of bed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 316948.0,
      "end_time": 320645.0,
      "text": "and that measure of sleep is what people call actigraphy."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 320670.0,
      "end_time": 321924.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s based on motion."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 323870.0,
      "end_time": 326381.0,
      "text": "But it turned out that we can actually get sleep"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 326405.0,
      "end_time": 328792.0,
      "text": "at a much more important level."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 328816.0,
      "end_time": 332380.0,
      "text": "We can understand the change in the brain waves"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 332404.0,
      "end_time": 333952.0,
      "text": "that occur during sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 335403.0,
      "end_time": 338356.0,
      "text": "So, many of you probably know that as we go to sleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 338380.0,
      "end_time": 341753.0,
      "text": "our brainwaves change and we enter different stages:"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 341777.0,
      "end_time": 345846.0,
      "text": "awake, light sleep, deep sleep and REM, or rapid eye movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 346267.0,
      "end_time": 350601.0,
      "text": "These stages are of course related to sleep disorders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 350625.0,
      "end_time": 353735.0,
      "text": "but they are also related to various diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 353759.0,
      "end_time": 359220.0,
      "text": "So for example, disturbances in REM are associated with depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 359718.0,
      "end_time": 363646.0,
      "text": "Disturbances in deep sleep are associated with Alzheimer&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 364614.0,
      "end_time": 367152.0,
      "text": "So if you want to get sleep staging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 367177.0,
      "end_time": 369487.0,
      "text": "today, you will send the person to the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 369511.0,
      "end_time": 372650.0,
      "text": "they put all of these electrodes on their head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 372890.0,
      "end_time": 373919.0,
      "text": "and they ask them to sleep like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 373943.0,
      "end_time": 376300.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 376270.0,
      "end_time": 378962.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not really a happy experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 380155.0,
      "end_time": 383900.0,
      "text": "So what if I tell you that I can do the same thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 383115.0,
      "end_time": 386282.0,
      "text": "but without any of these electrodes on the person&#39;s body?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 387596.0,
      "end_time": 389468.0,
      "text": "So here is our device,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 389492.0,
      "end_time": 392254.0,
      "text": "transmitting very low power wireless signal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 392278.0,
      "end_time": 394390.0,
      "text": "analyzes the reflections using AI"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 394414.0,
      "end_time": 397580.0,
      "text": "and spits out the sleep stages throughout the night."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 398647.0,
      "end_time": 402229.0,
      "text": "So we know, for example, when this person is dreaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 404333.0,
      "end_time": 405483.0,
      "text": "Not just that ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 406691.0,
      "end_time": 409777.0,
      "text": "we can even get your breathing while you are sitting like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 409802.0,
      "end_time": 411375.0,
      "text": "and without touching you."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 411399.0,
      "end_time": 413100.0,
      "text": "So he is sitting and reading"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 413250.0,
      "end_time": 415969.0,
      "text": "and this is his inhales, exhales."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 415994.0,
      "end_time": 417985.0,
      "text": "We asked him to hold his breath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 418900.0,
      "end_time": 420875.0,
      "text": "and you see the signal staying at a steady level"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 420899.0,
      "end_time": 422500.0,
      "text": "because he exhaled."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 422740.0,
      "end_time": 423224.0,
      "text": "He did not inhale."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 425279.0,
      "end_time": 427763.0,
      "text": "And I want to zoom in on the signal."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 427787.0,
      "end_time": 429849.0,
      "text": "And this is the same signal as before."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 429874.0,
      "end_time": 431555.0,
      "text": "These are the inhales,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 431579.0,
      "end_time": 433223.0,
      "text": "these are the exhales."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 433247.0,
      "end_time": 435334.0,
      "text": "And you see these blips on the signal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 435358.0,
      "end_time": 436669.0,
      "text": "These are not noise."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 437159.0,
      "end_time": 438938.0,
      "text": "They are his heartbeats."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 439971.0,
      "end_time": 441772.0,
      "text": "And you can see them beat by beat."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 443439.0,
      "end_time": 447660.0,
      "text": "So I want to stop here for a moment and show you a live demo."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 447684.0,
      "end_time": 449755.0,
      "text": "Zach is going to help me with the demo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 449779.0,
      "end_time": 454534.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going to use the device to monitor Zach&#39;s breathing."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 455272.0,
      "end_time": 459390.0,
      "text": "So this white box that you see here is the device,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 459640.0,
      "end_time": 461405.0,
      "text": "and Zach is turning it on ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 463581.0,
      "end_time": 466122.0,
      "text": "and I see that he breathes well."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 466146.0,
      "end_time": 470748.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to do exactly what we did in the video with the other guy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 470772.0,
      "end_time": 473462.0,
      "text": "so the wireless signal is going through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 473487.0,
      "end_time": 475137.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s touching Zach&#39;s body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 475161.0,
      "end_time": 477384.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s reflecting back to the device,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 477408.0,
      "end_time": 480779.0,
      "text": "and we want to monitor his breathing, his inhale-exhale motion."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 480803.0,
      "end_time": 483326.0,
      "text": "So we see the inhales, exhales --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 483350.0,
      "end_time": 487723.0,
      "text": "so see, these ups and downs are Zach breathing."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 490191.0,
      "end_time": 492342.0,
      "text": "Inhaling, exhaling."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 492366.0,
      "end_time": 497967.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 497992.0,
      "end_time": 500144.0,
      "text": "So, he can breathe."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 500168.0,
      "end_time": 501589.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 501613.0,
      "end_time": 503811.0,
      "text": "Zach, can you hold your breath, please?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 505216.0,
      "end_time": 508279.0,
      "text": "OK, so now he&#39;s holding his breath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 508303.0,
      "end_time": 510557.0,
      "text": "so you see the signal stays at a steady level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 510581.0,
      "end_time": 512207.0,
      "text": "and these are his heartbeats."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 512231.0,
      "end_time": 515707.0,
      "text": "Beat, beat, beat, beat, beat."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 515731.0,
      "end_time": 516732.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 516756.0,
      "end_time": 518923.0,
      "text": "OK, Zach, you can breathe again."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 518947.0,
      "end_time": 520836.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 520860.0,
      "end_time": 522280.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t want accidents here."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 522304.0,
      "end_time": 523304.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 523328.0,
      "end_time": 524478.0,
      "text": "OK, thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 525756.0,
      "end_time": 531692.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 531716.0,
      "end_time": 534477.0,
      "text": "So as you can see, we have this device"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 534501.0,
      "end_time": 538400.0,
      "text": "that can monitor so many physiological signals for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 538650.0,
      "end_time": 541250.0,
      "text": "and what is really interesting about this device"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 541490.0,
      "end_time": 543612.0,
      "text": "is that it does all this without any wearables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 543636.0,
      "end_time": 546334.0,
      "text": "without asking the person to change his behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 546358.0,
      "end_time": 548849.0,
      "text": "or to wear anything or charge anything special."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 549739.0,
      "end_time": 552707.0,
      "text": "And that got doctors very excited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 552731.0,
      "end_time": 553882.0,
      "text": "because doctors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 553906.0,
      "end_time": 556863.0,
      "text": "they always want to know more information about their patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 556887.0,
      "end_time": 558560.0,
      "text": "particularly at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 558810.0,
      "end_time": 560715.0,
      "text": "and this is particularly true in chronic diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 560739.0,
      "end_time": 564894.0,
      "text": "like pulmonary diseases, like COPD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 564918.0,
      "end_time": 569442.0,
      "text": "or heart failure or Alzheimer&#39;s and even depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 569466.0,
      "end_time": 571783.0,
      "text": "All of these chronic diseases are very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 571807.0,
      "end_time": 574275.0,
      "text": "In fact -- perhaps you know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 574299.0,
      "end_time": 577179.0,
      "text": "two-thirds of the cost of health care in the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 577203.0,
      "end_time": 579187.0,
      "text": "is due to chronic diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 579545.0,
      "end_time": 582750.0,
      "text": "But what is really interesting about chronic diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 582100.0,
      "end_time": 583920.0,
      "text": "is that when the person, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 583944.0,
      "end_time": 588680.0,
      "text": "has a problem that leads to the hospital and the emergency room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 588705.0,
      "end_time": 591200.0,
      "text": "this problem doesn&#39;t happen overnight."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 591440.0,
      "end_time": 593122.0,
      "text": "Actually, things happen gradually."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 593147.0,
      "end_time": 596869.0,
      "text": "So if we can monitor chronic disease patients in their home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 596893.0,
      "end_time": 601154.0,
      "text": "we can detect changes in their breathing, heartbeat, mobility, sleep --"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 601178.0,
      "end_time": 605360.0,
      "text": "and we can detect emergencies before they occur"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 605384.0,
      "end_time": 607701.0,
      "text": "and have the doctor intervene earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 607725.0,
      "end_time": 609788.0,
      "text": "so that we can avoid hospitalization."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 610645.0,
      "end_time": 614747.0,
      "text": "And indeed, today we are working with multiple doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 614771.0,
      "end_time": 616729.0,
      "text": "in different disease categories."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 616754.0,
      "end_time": 617937.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m really excited"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 617961.0,
      "end_time": 620645.0,
      "text": "because we have deployed the device with many patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 620669.0,
      "end_time": 624100.0,
      "text": "We have deployed the device with patients that have COPD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 624250.0,
      "end_time": 625531.0,
      "text": "which is a pulmonary disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 625556.0,
      "end_time": 627611.0,
      "text": "patients that have Alzheimer&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 627635.0,
      "end_time": 629928.0,
      "text": "patients that have depression and anxiety"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 629952.0,
      "end_time": 631667.0,
      "text": "and people that have Parkinson&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 632798.0,
      "end_time": 635681.0,
      "text": "And we are working with the doctors on improving their life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 635705.0,
      "end_time": 637546.0,
      "text": "understanding the disease better."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 638718.0,
      "end_time": 641289.0,
      "text": "So when I started, I told you"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 641313.0,
      "end_time": 646733.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m really fascinated with Star Wars and the Force in Star Wars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 646757.0,
      "end_time": 650830.0,
      "text": "and indeed, I&#39;m still very much fascinated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 650107.0,
      "end_time": 652113.0,
      "text": "even now, as a grown-up, with Star Wars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 652137.0,
      "end_time": 654431.0,
      "text": "waiting for the next movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 654456.0,
      "end_time": 659725.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m very fascinated now and excited"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 659749.0,
      "end_time": 663547.0,
      "text": "about this new Force of wireless signals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 663571.0,
      "end_time": 667577.0,
      "text": "and the potential of changing health care with this new force."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 667601.0,
      "end_time": 670545.0,
      "text": "One of the patients with whom we deployed is actually my aunt."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 670569.0,
      "end_time": 672719.0,
      "text": "She has heart failure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 672744.0,
      "end_time": 676452.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m sure many of you guys in the audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 676476.0,
      "end_time": 681164.0,
      "text": "have parents, grandparents, loved ones who have chronic diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 681188.0,
      "end_time": 684450.0,
      "text": "So I want you to imagine with me a future"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 684700.0,
      "end_time": 686952.0,
      "text": "where in every home that has a chronic disease patient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 686976.0,
      "end_time": 690101.0,
      "text": "there is a device like this device sitting in the background"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 690125.0,
      "end_time": 692490.0,
      "text": "and just monitoring passively"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 692514.0,
      "end_time": 697180.0,
      "text": "sleep, breathing, the health of this chronic disease patient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 697204.0,
      "end_time": 699328.0,
      "text": "and before an emergency occurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 699352.0,
      "end_time": 702375.0,
      "text": "it would detect the degradation in the physiological signal"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 702399.0,
      "end_time": 703899.0,
      "text": "and alert the doctor"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 703923.0,
      "end_time": 705986.0,
      "text": "so that we can avoid hospitalization."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 706652.0,
      "end_time": 709779.0,
      "text": "This can change health care as we know it today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 709803.0,
      "end_time": 712803.0,
      "text": "improve how we understand chronic diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 712827.0,
      "end_time": 714596.0,
      "text": "and also save many lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 714898.0,
      "end_time": 716490.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 716730.0,
      "end_time": 721207.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 721231.0,
      "end_time": 723117.0,
      "text": "Helen Walters: Dina, thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 723142.0,
      "end_time": 724293.0,
      "text": "Thank you too, Zach."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 724317.0,
      "end_time": 725628.0,
      "text": "So glad you&#39;re breathing."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 725652.0,
      "end_time": 728349.0,
      "text": "So Dina, this is amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 728373.0,
      "end_time": 731401.0,
      "text": "The positive applications are incredible."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 731425.0,
      "end_time": 735420.0,
      "text": "What is the framework, though, like the ethical framework around this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 735444.0,
      "end_time": 738324.0,
      "text": "What are you doing to prevent this technology from being used"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 738348.0,
      "end_time": 742117.0,
      "text": "for other, perhaps less positive types of applications?"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 742141.0,
      "end_time": 745195.0,
      "text": "Dina Katabi: Yeah, this is a very important question, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 745220.0,
      "end_time": 746389.0,
      "text": "like, what about misuse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 746413.0,
      "end_time": 750350.0,
      "text": "or what about, I guess you could say, about the Dark Side of the Force?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 750590.0,
      "end_time": 751233.0,
      "text": "HW: Right, right."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 751257.0,
      "end_time": 753343.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 753368.0,
      "end_time": 756867.0,
      "text": "DK: So we actually have technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 756891.0,
      "end_time": 761168.0,
      "text": "that prevent people from trying to use this device"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 761192.0,
      "end_time": 763546.0,
      "text": "to monitor somebody without their consent."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 763570.0,
      "end_time": 765823.0,
      "text": "Because the device understands space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 765847.0,
      "end_time": 769268.0,
      "text": "it will ask you to prove, by doing certain movements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 769292.0,
      "end_time": 771470.0,
      "text": "that you have access to the space"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 771710.0,
      "end_time": 774371.0,
      "text": "and you are the person who you are asking the device to monitor."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 774395.0,
      "end_time": 776585.0,
      "text": "So technology-wise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 776609.0,
      "end_time": 779997.0,
      "text": "we have technology that we integrate to prevent misuse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 780210.0,
      "end_time": 783911.0,
      "text": "but also, I think there is a role for policy, like everything else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 783935.0,
      "end_time": 789371.0,
      "text": "and hopefully, with the two of them, we can control any misuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 789395.0,
      "end_time": 790952.0,
      "text": "HW: Amazing. Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 790976.0,
      "end_time": 792127.0,
      "text": "DK: Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 792151.0,
      "end_time": 795920.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}